<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title><%= title %></title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body {
      background-color: #f9fafc;
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
    }
    .hero {
      background: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.6), rgba(0,0,0,0.6)),
                  url("https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1517649763962-0c623066013b?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1500&q=80");
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center;
      color: white;
      padding: 100px 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 3rem;
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    .content {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 60px auto;
      background: white;
      padding: 40px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    .content h2 {
      color: #007bff;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <section class="hero">
    <h1>About KhelKhooj</h1>
    <p>Connecting athletes with top-tier sports academies across India.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="content text-center">
    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
    <p>At KhelKhooj, our mission is to bridge the gap between aspiring athletes and the best sports training academies. We believe that every talented sportsperson deserves an opportunity to showcase their skills and receive world-class guidance.</p>
    
    <h2>What We Offer</h2>
    <p>We help athletes find, connect, and grow under reputed sports academies offering facilities in Cricket, Football, and Athletics.</p>

    <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary mt-3">Back to Home</a>
  </section>

</body>
</html>
